## File Access Boundaries

**Read & Write Freely:**
- `engine/src/` â€” backend logic
- `portal/src/` â€” frontend components
- `.docs/` â€” project documentation
- Any other source code directories

**Read Only:**
- All sibling repos in multi-repo projects (never edit them â€” author in the parent repo's `.flux-group/`)

**Never Touch:**
- `.flux/` â€” ticket files (in-repo mode)
- `.flux-store/` â€” ticket files (orphan mode)
- `.flux/config.json` â€” use `get_board_config` MCP tool instead

