## Ticket Model

Tickets have these fields (used in MCP tool calls):

| Field | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | string | e.g. `FLUX-41` (auto-assigned, never change) |
| `title` | string | Short description |
| `status` | string | Board column: `Grooming`, `Todo`, `In Progress`, `Ready`, `Done`, `Released` |
| `priority` | string | `None`, `Low`, `Medium`, `High`, `Critical` |
| `effort` | string | `None`, `XS`, `S`, `M`, `L`, `XL` |
| `assignee` | string | User name or `unassigned` |
| `tags` | string[] | From board config |
| `body` | markdown | Description & implementation plan |
| `subtasks` | string[] | Child ticket IDs |
| `implementationLink` | string | Commit hash or PR URL (set by `finish_ticket`) |
| `branch` | string | Git branch name (e.g. `flux/FLUX-41-add-field`) |
| `history` | array | Read-only append-only event log (comments, status changes, activity) |

