## End-to-End Checklist

Before marking a ticket `Ready` or `Done`:

- âś… Ticket read fully â€” relevant docs reviewed
- âś… Implementation plan posted as a comment (use `add_comment`)
- âś… Status moved at the right time (never skip status transitions)
- âś… Code changes validated (run tests, start the app, verify behavior)
- âś… Docs updated (`.docs/` matches new behavior; completion comment says so explicitly)
- âś… Questions went through `Require Input` status, not only chat
- âś… Findings persisted via MCP tools, not left in chat or agent memory

